{"id":42,"ayahs":[{"number":253,"arabic":"۞ تِلْكَ ٱلرُّسُلُ فَضَّلْنَا بَعْضَهُمْ عَلَىٰ بَعْضٍۢ ۘ مِّنْهُم مَّن كَلَّمَ ٱللَّهُ ۖ وَرَفَعَ بَعْضَهُمْ دَرَجَٰتٍۢ ۚ وَءَاتَيْنَا عِيسَى ٱبْنَ مَرْيَمَ ٱلْبَيِّنَٰتِ وَأَيَّدْنَٰهُ بِرُوحِ ٱلْقُدُسِ ۗ وَلَوْ شَآءَ ٱللَّهُ مَا ٱقْتَتَلَ ٱلَّذِينَ مِنۢ بَعْدِهِم مِّنۢ بَعْدِ مَا جَآءَتْهُمُ ٱلْبَيِّنَٰتُ وَلَٰكِنِ ٱخْتَلَفُوا۟ فَمِنْهُم مَّنْ ءَامَنَ وَمِنْهُم مَّن كَفَرَ ۚ وَلَوْ شَآءَ ٱللَّهُ مَا ٱقْتَتَلُوا۟ وَلَٰكِنَّ ٱللَّهَ يَفْعَلُ مَا يُرِيدُ","translation":"Some of these apostles have We endowed more highly than others: among them were such as were spoken to by God [Himself], and some He has raised yet higher.' And We vouchsafed unto Jesus, the son of Mary, all evidence of the truth, and strengthened him with holy inspiration. And if God had so willed, they who succeeded those [apostles] would not have contended with one another after all evidence of the truth had come to them; but [as it was,] they did take to divergent views, and some of them attained to faith, while some of them came to deny the truth. Yet if God had so willed, they would not have contended with one another: but God does whatever He wills.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/260.mp3","surahId":2,"words":[{"id":87067,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ تِلْكَ","translation":"এই","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87068,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱلرُّسُلُ","translation":"রাসূলগণ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87069,"position":3,"arabic":"فَضَّلْنَا","translation":"আমরা মর্যাদা দিয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87070,"position":4,"arabic":"بَعْضَهُمْ","translation":"তাদের কাউকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87071,"position":5,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87072,"position":6,"arabic":"بَعْضٍۢ ۘ","translation":"কারও","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87074,"position":7,"arabic":"مِّنْهُم","translation":"তাদের মধ্যে হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87075,"position":8,"arabic":"مَّن","translation":"কারও (সাথে)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87076,"position":9,"arabic":"كَلَّمَ","translation":"বলেছেন কথা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87077,"position":10,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ ۖ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87079,"position":11,"arabic":"وَرَفَعَ","translation":"এবং উন্নীত করেছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87080,"position":12,"arabic":"بَعْضَهُمْ","translation":"তাদের কাউকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87081,"position":13,"arabic":"دَرَجَـٰتٍۢ ۚ","translation":"(উচ্চ) মর্যাদায়","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87083,"position":14,"arabic":"وَءَاتَيْنَا","translation":"এবং আমরা দিয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87084,"position":15,"arabic":"عِيسَى","translation":"ঈসাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87085,"position":16,"arabic":"ٱبْنَ","translation":"পুত্র","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87086,"position":17,"arabic":"مَرْيَمَ","translation":"মারইয়ামের","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87087,"position":18,"arabic":"ٱلْبَيِّنَـٰتِ","translation":"সুষ্পষ্ট প্রমাণ সমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87088,"position":19,"arabic":"وَأَيَّدْنَـٰهُ","translation":"এবং তাকে সাহায্য করেছি আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87089,"position":20,"arabic":"بِرُوحِ","translation":"আত্মা দিয়ে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87090,"position":21,"arabic":"ٱلْقُدُسِ ۗ","translation":"পবিত্র (অর্থাৎ জিবরাইল)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87092,"position":22,"arabic":"وَلَوْ","translation":"এবং যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87093,"position":23,"arabic":"شَآءَ","translation":"চাইতেন","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87094,"position":24,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87095,"position":25,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_030.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87096,"position":26,"arabic":"ٱقْتَتَلَ","translation":"তারা পরস্পর যুদ্ধ করত","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_031.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87097,"position":27,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"যারা (ছিল)","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_032.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87098,"position":28,"arabic":"مِنۢ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_033.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87099,"position":29,"arabic":"بَعْدِهِم","translation":"তাদের পরে","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_034.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87100,"position":30,"arabic":"مِّنۢ","translation":"থেকেও","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_035.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87101,"position":31,"arabic":"بَعْدِ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_036.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87102,"position":32,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_037.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87103,"position":33,"arabic":"جَآءَتْهُمُ","translation":"তাদের কাছে এসেছিল","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_038.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87104,"position":34,"arabic":"ٱلْبَيِّنَـٰتُ","translation":"সুষ্পষ্ট নিদর্শনাদি","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_039.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87105,"position":35,"arabic":"وَلَـٰكِنِ","translation":"কিন্তু","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_040.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87106,"position":36,"arabic":"ٱخْتَلَفُوا۟","translation":"মতবিরোধ করল তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/002_253_041.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":87107,"position":37,"arabic":"فَمِنْهُم","tr